<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She always looks sensational whenever she steps out.</p>

<p>And Lizzie Cundy sizzled as she stepped out in Chelsea, London, for dinner with Niccolo Barattieri who has previously been linked to model Elizabeth Hurley on Tuesday.</p>

<p>The TV personality, 52, put on a very leggy display in a leather mini skirt which accentuated her toned physique as she left restaurant La Famiglia.</p>

<p>Wow! Lizzie Cundy put on a leggy display in a leather mini skirt  as she stepped out for dinner with Niccolo Barattieri on Tuesday</p>

<p>Lizzie cut a stylish figure in her all-black ensemble and added some extra height to her trim frame with a pair of mesh heels.</p>

<p>She completed her look with a semi-sheer polka-dot top which flashed a peak at her washboard abs.</p>

<p>The beauty wore her caramel tresses gently curled and let them bounce over her shoulders as she strutted out of the restaurant and into a car.</p>

<p>While Lizzie's dinner companion Niccolo also dressed up for the occasion, putting on a dapper display in a crisp white shirt and navy blue chinos.</p>

<p>Looking good: The beauty added some extra height to her frame with a pair of mesh heels which tied up the front</p>

<p>Glowing: Lizzie added a slick of pink lipstick to accentuate her pretty features for the outing</p>

<p>Niccolo has previously been linked to model Elizabeth Hurley after they were spotted having dinner together in Mayfair back in 2018.</p>

<p>His white Maserati was also said to be spotted regularly outside her Chelsea home at the time.</p>

<p>The Italian property developer previously dated Princess Diana's niece Lady Kitty Spencer however they split in 2017.</p>

<p>It comes after Lizzie was forced to cancel her usual lavish plans for her birthday as she marked her 52nd during lockdown in May. </p>

<p>Dapper: The TV personality was joined by Niccolo Barattieri who previously dated Liz Hurley</p>

<p>Stunning: Lizzie flashed her washboard abs in a semi-sheer crop top</p>

<p>All in the details: She added a selection of pretty bracelets to add some sparkle to her look</p>

<p>Off he goes: Niccolo donned navy chinos and a smart jacket for the dinner with Lizzie</p>

<p>Smooth: The Italian businessman ensured her was well groomed and wore her blonde locks swept to one side</p>

<p>However in true Lizzie style, she promised a huge party once life returns to normal with the proceeds from the bash going to the National Health Service. </p>

<p>Speaking exclusively to MailOnline, she said: I really want to give back and say thank you to the NHS as they have been so incredible and I’m so thankful to have got through the coronavirus myself</p>

<p>'I’m so sad not to be with my family and friends and especially be with my son on my special day but know we will all be together soon...</p>

<p>'Good times are in their way ! I want my party to be the biggest fund raiser for the NHS to give thanks!'</p>

<p>Poser: Lizzie made sure to work all of her angles as she sat in the car</p>

<p>Work it: Lizzie wore her caramel tresses down and let them cascade over her shoulders</p>

<p>Leggy: The beauty highlighted her toned pins in the tiny leather skirt </p>
